    "In the UPGRADE mode, if the new solution does not violate O1, the diff is between the value O2 of the two solutions; otherwise, the solution is dropped.",
    "The probability of acceptance also depends on the value of temperature T that decreases over iterations by a reduction factor.",
    "The effectiveness of SA depends on the initial value of T, the minimum temperature T min, and the temperature reduction factor.",
    "In our simulation, we found the initial value of T = 0.0125, T min = 0.0005 and = 0.99 offers decent performance.",
    "Note that the accuracy value of a solution is in the range [0, 1]."
